      "author": "dzake 2",
      "published_date": "2008-08-01T00:00:00.000Z",
      "text": "As Approved by TAC on 05/08/08 \nElectric Reliability Organization Fee Assessment and Collection Guide \nTable of Contents \n1 Electric Reliability Organization Authority..................................................................................................2\n2 North American Electric Reliability Corporation Budgeting Process........................................................2\n2.1 NERC Budgeting Process........................................................................................................................2\n2.2 Annual Fee Notification ..........................................................................................................................2\n3 Calculation of the Electric Reliability Organization Fee .............................................................................2\n3.1 Calculation of Electric Reliability Organization Fee...............................................................................2\n3.1.1 Net Energy for Load (Adjust",
